684
00:47:30,076 --> 00:47:31,421
Hyun Young.

685
00:47:32,619 --> 00:47:34,746
Ja?

686
00:47:34,746 --> 00:47:36,283
Lasst uns aufhören.

687
00:47:36,283 --> 00:47:37,832
